@startuml
title System Components & Interactions (No Daily GrowthLog)

actor User
rectangle "API / Orchestrator" as ORCH
rectangle "LLMInterface\n(ainvoke)" as LLM
rectangle "Injector\n(순수 로직)" as INJ
rectangle "Generator\n(Celery Task)" as GEN
rectangle "Sniffer (Shared)\n공용 트렌드 인덱스" as SNIFF
rectangle "Synchro\n(개인화 임베딩/RAG)" as SYNC
rectangle "Adapter(s)\nThreads 등" as ADPT
rectangle "Scheduler\n(Celery Beat/Worker)" as SCH
rectangle "CoWorker\n(이메일 루프/Playbook On-demand)" as COW
database "DB (Postgres/pgvector)" as DB
collections "Redis\n(broker/cache/idem)" as REDIS

User --> ORCH : 요청(지시사항/저장/발행/조회 등)

ORCH ..> SNIFF : 공용 트렌드 조회(READ)
ORCH ..> SYNC : 개인화 컨텍스트/임베딩 조회(READ)
ORCH ..> ADPT : constraints 조회(READ)
ORCH --> INJ : persona + trends + playbook + constraints
INJ --> GEN : brief/meta 전달 (task enqueue)
GEN ..> LLM : ainvoke(지시사항 생성)
GEN --> ORCH : 지시사항 JSON 반환

ORCH --> DB : Draft/Metadata 저장
ORCH --> SYNC : ingest 요청(임베딩 갱신, 비동기)

ORCH --> SCH : 발행/모니터링 스케줄 생성
SCH --> ADPT : publish()/fetch_metrics()
ADPT --> SYNC : 모니터링 결과 ingest(비동기)

ORCH --> COW : Playbook 생성/갱신 요청(On-demand)
COW ..> SNIFF : 트렌드 참조(공용)
COW ..> SYNC : 계정 컨텍스트 조회(선택)
COW ..> ADPT : 활성 캠페인·주제 적합성 확인(READ)
COW --> DB : Playbook 저장(계정 단위)
COW --> User : 이메일 발송(조건 충족 시 1일 1회)

ORCH ..> REDIS
SCH ..> REDIS
GEN ..> REDIS
@enduml
